net.cloud.client.file.request

Class LoadRequest<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.client.file.request.FileRequest<T>
      • net.cloud.client.file.request.LoadRequest<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the object used to represent the file
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BufferedReaderRequest, CachedFileRegionRequest, CachedFileRequest, RandomAccessFileLoadRequest, XmlLoadRequest

    public abstract class LoadRequest<T>
extends FileRequest<T>
    A FileRequest which in particular is requesting that a file be loaded and prepared for reading from. While there is no outright guarantee that subclasses will enforce that the returned file is read-only, this is the suggested purpose.
